# Security Checklist
# =====================================================================
# Before going to production:
# [x] Generate strong JWT_SECRET (min 32 characters)
# [x] Use production Supabase project (not development)
# [x] Change default user passwords
# [x] Enable CORS with specific frontend URL
# [x] Verify all migrations ran successfully
# [x] Test all API endpoints
